{{see|zloty}}
==Polish==

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|zwɔtɨ}}

===Noun===
'''złoty''', '''złote''' {{p}} (if the number ends with 2-4, apart from 11-14), '''[[złotych]]''' {{p}} (if the number ends with 0, 1, 5-9 or 11-14)

# [[zloty]] (''the currency of [[Poland]]'')
# {{heraldry}} [[or]], the color of gold

===Adjective===
'''złoty''' 

# in the color of [[gold]], [[golden]]
# made from [[gold]]
# containig gold

